Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.32,0:00:03.87,Default,Lain,0,0,0,,You are a counselor and a psychiatrist, Touko-san?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:04.54,0:00:07.35,Default,Lain,0,0,0,,And a psychiatrist is someone who heals mental illnesses?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.80,0:00:16.20,Default,Touko,0,0,0,,Uh huh. Put simply, I’m a doctor of the mind. As I mentioned before, mental illness is very complex.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.04,0:00:19.96,Default,Lain,0,0,0,,What is mental illness?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.40,0:00:29.50,Default,Touko,0,0,0,,Basically, a person’s mind becomes disturbed for some reason, and the person is unable to continue functioning.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.39,0:00:33.10,Default,Lain,0,0,0,,What sort of reason, for instance?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.18,0:00:35.36,Default,Touko,0,0,0,,There can be many reasons.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.91,0:00:42.44,Default,Touko,0,0,0,,Problems with a living environment or work environment can be reasons.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.10,0:00:45.60,Default,Touko,0,0,0,,Sudden, psychological shock can also be a reason.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.04,0:00:51.28,Default,Touko,0,0,0,,The sudden death of a well-loved pet can trigger mental illness.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.18,0:00:56.31,Default,Touko,0,0,0,,Sometimes people become mentally ill because of something that happens to them physically.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.22,0:01:00.06,Default,Touko,0,0,0,,A car accident or some other kind of physical trauma can be a cause.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.54,0:01:03.74,Default,Touko,0,0,0,,Also, people who drink too much can damage the function of their brains.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.35,0:01:05.56,Default,Lain,0,0,0,,Alcoholism?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.83,0:01:06.32,Default,Touko,0,0,0,,Exactly.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.54,0:01:07.76,Default,Touko,0,0,0,,You’ve been studying!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.84,0:01:12.95,Default,Touko,0,0,0,,If you drink too much, the alcohol content in your blood will rise.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.55,0:01:16.51,Default,Touko,0,0,0,,You’ve seen drunk people wobble around without balance, haven’t you?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.42,0:01:20.99,Default,Touko,0,0,0,,They’re in an alcoholic stupor.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.70,0:01:24.08,Default,Lain,0,0,0,,But normal people aren’t that way, are they?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:24.32,0:01:25.68,Default,Touko,0,0,0,,No, they can be.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.22,0:01:29.55,Default,Touko,0,0,0,,It takes about 24 hours for alcohol to leave the human body.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.48,0:01:39.03,Default,Touko,0,0,0,,If you drink a lot everyday for a year or so—if you stay drunk long enough—your perception will start to change.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.96,0:01:43.20,Default,Touko,0,0,0,,Your brain will start to deteriorate.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.76,0:01:44.56,Default,Lain,0,0,0,,That’s scary.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.74,0:01:49.10,Default,Touko,0,0,0,,It is scary. I still have some sake now and then, though.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.90,0:01:50.84,Default,Lain,0,0,0,,Isn’t that dangerous?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.28,0:01:51.59,Default,Touko,0,0,0,,Ha, ha.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.67,0:01:52.42,Default,Touko,0,0,0,,Oh, a little bit.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.44,0:01:54.92,Default,Touko,0,0,0,,And smoking is bad, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.23,0:01:58.74,Default,Touko,0,0,0,,But having a drink with friends every now and then can help relieve stress.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.75,0:02:04.28,Default,Touko,0,0,0,,Relieving stress is very important for the body’s health.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.22,0:02:08.14,Default,Lain,0,0,0,,I don’t understand what stress is.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.95,0:02:12.76,Default,Touko,0,0,0,,Remember when you didn’t like coming here at first?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.46,0:02:13.80,Default,Lain,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.24,0:02:17.86,Default,Touko,0,0,0,,Stress is what we call the cause of that discomfort.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.90,0:02:20.90,Default,Touko,0,0,0,,You’re glad that the discomfort is gone, aren’t you?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.90,0:02:23.31,Default,Lain,0,0,0,,Yes. What other kinds of mental illness are there?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.23,0:02:29.14,Default,Touko,0,0,0,,Could you excuse me? I’ve been talking so much and I’m a little thirsty.
